    <h2>wizard.js Controller</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>VB includes <code>wizard.js</code>, a lightweight controller that enhances <code>form[data-wizard]</code> elements with step navigation, validation, conditional steps, and progress tracking. It works as a standard form without JavaScript (progressive enhancement).</p>
    </layout-text>

    <h3>Basic Setup</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Add <code>data-wizard</code> to a form. Each <code>&lt;fieldset data-wizard-step&gt;</code> becomes a step. The controller auto-initializes on <code>DOMContentLoaded</code>.</p>
